    Laptops on Sale

    A new laptop could mean newer opportunities if youve reached a point where an upgrade will open the door for you. Take your pick based on the laptop deals available, spanning a wide range that covers everything from Windows, Mac, and Chromebooks. Laptop deals include various screen sizes and internal specs, giving you the tools you need to get things done. There are 2-in-1 laptops that function like tablets when you detach or flip them over, where you can also use a stylus to write or draw on the screen. Best Buy has you covered with laptops on sale this holiday season, no matter the type, brand, or price you have in mind.

    What types of laptops go on sale at Best Buy?

    Literally every type of laptop goes on sale at Best Buy. Check at any given time and youll see offerings from all the major brands, including ASUS laptops on sale, Apple MacBook sales, and a sale on HP laptops.

    Sales also cover all different categories. Typically, the cheapest laptops on sale will be Chromebooks and used laptops on sale. But youll always find savings on the latest 2-in-1 convertibles, gaming laptops, super-sized productivity powerhouses, mini laptops on sale, rugged laptops, Apple laptops, touchscreen laptops, refurbished laptops and even open box models. Youll also find savings from Best Buy Marketplace sellers.

    In other words, no matter what kind of laptop or what brand youre interested in, youll find a huge selection of laptops that are on sale to choose from.

    When do sales on laptops take place?

    Best Buy is known for its big annual events like the Boxing Day sale on laptops, Cyber Monday savings, and the laptops on sale for Black Friday. While these are marquee events that many people wait for, you should know that Best Buy constantly has sales on laptops.

    Every week, youll find a large selection of laptops on sale online and in-store, from all your favourite brands.

    In addition, with new models arriving regularly from manufacturers, there are always laptops on clearance sales to make room for the latest and greatest. This includes models powered by the newest processors like Intel Core Ultra and AMD Ryzen 8000 Series, and even the latest Copilot+ PCs with built-in AI features.

    What type of savings are there for laptops that are on sale?

    Shoppers can save considerably when they choose laptops that are on sale at Best Buy. The amount will obviously vary based on the type of laptop and its original retail price, but even the cheapest laptops on sale represent significant savings.

    Best Buy often goes beyond saving money on the purchase of the laptop itself. Look for additional savings promotions that can include offers like discounted accessories such as hard drives, keyboards, printers, or extended warranties with a qualifying laptop purchase.

    How can I be notified of laptops on sale?

    You can check our website at any time to see Best Buy laptops on sale or check the weekly Top Deals. But the easiest way to be notified of the latest laptops at Best Buy on sale is to sign up for our e-mail list. Youll receive an immediate notification so you can get a head start, whether you choose to shop in-store or online.

    For even more limited-time offers, explore our Black Friday in Summer laptop deals and other seasonal savings events.

    Shop products that are brand new, open box, and/or refurbished. Whichever you choose, shop confidently knowing that all open box and refurbished products have been fully inspected for 100% functionality and come with a warranty. Plus, they're a great way to save on the latest tech.
    RAM, or short-term storage, acts like a desk space for temporary data the computer needs to do its job efficiently. 8GB works for general tasks, while 16GB to 32GB is ideal for demanding workloads. 64GB and up support content creation and other large-scale tasks.
    Size of the screen, in inches, measured diagonally from corner to corner. A 15-inch screen or larger offers more space for open tasks, while a device with a smaller screen is typically lighter and more portable.
    As the brain network of the computer, the processor instructs other parts what to do and at what speed. The higher the model number across a brand, the more brain power for multitasking and complex tasks.
    The hard drive is your computer's long-term storage and acts like a cabinet for files, documents, and other data you'll need the next time you turn on your computer. 250GB is good for basic storage, while 1TB holds expansive data and games. 2TB or more is ideal for content creators.
    The OS manages all software and hardware, including files, memory and connected devices. It also lets you interact with your computer and programs in a visual way, instead of typing computer code.
    The core is an individual processing unit that runs a particular task in a processor. Additional cores enable the computer to run more smoothly and perform tasks faster.
